# Wiki text layer only — the heavy binary archive (per-ticker filings, decks,
# audio, briefings, equity calls, reports) stays UNtracked. Rollback safety net
# for the _wiki synthesis + derived feature artifacts only.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/.gitattributes
!/INDEX.md
!/_wiki/
!/CLAUDE.md
!/automation/
!/.claude/
/.claude/*
!/.claude/settings.json
# throwaway previews inside _wiki
_wiki/_preview_*.html
__pycache__/
*.pyc
# full-corpus search index (binary, rebuilt by _tools/build_search_index.py)
_wiki/_data/search.db
_wiki/%TEMP%/
